class Persona:
     def __init__(self, name, age, gender, phone, languages, skills, hobbies):
          self.name = 'Wolfang Herrera'
          self.age = 21
          self.gender = 'male'
          self.phone = '+57 (313)-450 8305'
          self.languages = ['Spanish', 'English']
          self.skills = ['Python', 'Typescript' , 'AWS', 'Git', 'Scrum']
          self.hobbies = 'taking a walk with my dog and workout'

     def __str__(self):
          return f'Hey, I'm {{'{self.name}'}}, I'm {{'{self.age}'}} years old and in my free time,
                  I enjoy {{'{self.hobbies}'}}.'


print(Persona())
>>> Hey, I'm Wolfang Herrera, I'm 21 years old and in my free time, I enjoy taking a walk
    with my dog and workout.
